@* 通用銀行帳號 Tab — 支援客戶、廠商、員工、公司；根據 EntityType 動態載入對應銀行帳號 *@
@using ERPCore2.Models.Enums
@inject ICustomerBankAccountService CustomerBankAccountService
@inject ISupplierBankAccountService SupplierBankAccountService
@inject IEmployeeBankAccountService EmployeeBankAccountService
@inject ICompanyBankAccountService CompanyBankAccountService
@inject INotificationService NotificationService
@inject IStringLocalizer<SharedResource> L

<div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-2 px-1">
    <div class="d-flex gap-2">
        <GenericButtonComponent IconClass=
                                Variant="ButtonVariant.DarkBlue"
                                Text="@L["Button.AddBankAccount"]"
                                OnClick="@HandleAdd"
                                IsDisabled="@(!EntityId.HasValue)" />
    </div>
</div>

<GenericInteractiveTableComponent TItem="BankAccountRow"
                                  Items="@accounts"
                                  ColumnDefinitions="@GetColumnDefinitions()"
                                  ShowHeader="true"
                                  ShowRowNumbers="true"
                                  IsStriped="true"
                                  IsHoverable="true"
                                  IsBordered="true"
                                  IsReadOnly="true"
                                  ShowBuiltInActions="true"
                                  ShowBuiltInDeleteButton="false"
                                  EnableAutoEmptyRow="false"
                                  EmptyMessage="@L["Message.NoBankAccounts"]"
                                  CustomActionsTemplate="@GetActionsTemplate()"
                                  ActionsColumnWidth="100px" />

@* 銀行帳號編輯 Modal *@
<GenericBankAccountEditModalComponent EntityType="@EntityType"
                                      EntityId="@EntityId"
                                      BankAccountId="@editingId"
                                      IsVisible="@isModalVisible"
                                      IsVisibleChanged="@((bool v) => isModalVisible = v)"
                                      OnSaved="@HandleSaved"
                                      OnCancel="@(() => isModalVisible = false)" />

@code {
    [Parameter] public BankAccountEntityType EntityType { get; set; }
    [Parameter] public int? EntityId { get; set; }

    private record BankAccountRow(int Id, string? BankName, string? BranchName, string AccountNumber, string AccountName, bool IsPrimary, string? Purpose);

    private List<BankAccountRow> accounts = new();
    private bool isModalVisible = false;
    private int? editingId = null;
    private int _lastLoadedId;

    // ===== 欄位定義 =====

    private List<InteractiveColumnDefinition> GetColumnDefinitions()
    {
        var columns = new List<InteractiveColumnDefinition>
        {
            new()
            {
                Title = L["Field.BankName"],
                PropertyName = nameof(BankAccountRow.BankName),
                ColumnType = InteractiveColumnType.Display,
                Width = "120px",
                NullDisplayText = "-"
            },
            new()
            {
                Title = L["Field.BranchName"],
                PropertyName = nameof(BankAccountRow.BranchName),
                ColumnType = InteractiveColumnType.Display,
                Width = "120px",
                NullDisplayText = "-"
            },
            new()
            {
                Title = L["Field.AccountNumber"],
                PropertyName = nameof(BankAccountRow.AccountNumber),
                ColumnType = InteractiveColumnType.Display,
                Width = "140px"
            },
            new()
            {
                Title = L["Field.AccountName"],
                PropertyName = nameof(BankAccountRow.AccountName),
                ColumnType = InteractiveColumnType.Display
            }
        };

        if (EntityType == BankAccountEntityType.Company)
        {
            columns.Add(new()
            {
                Title = L["Field.Purpose"],
                PropertyName = nameof(BankAccountRow.Purpose),
                ColumnType = InteractiveColumnType.Display,
                NullDisplayText = "-"
            });
        }

        columns.Add(new()
        {
            Title = L["Field.IsPrimary"],
            PropertyName = nameof(BankAccountRow.IsPrimary),
            ColumnType = InteractiveColumnType.Display,
            Width = "200px",
            CellCssClass = "text-center",
            HeaderCssClass = "text-center",
            DisplayFormatter = item =>
            {
                if (item is BankAccountRow row && row.IsPrimary)
                    return $"<span class=\"badge bg-primary\">{L["Label.Primary"]}</span>";
                return "";
            }
        });

        return columns;
    }

    private RenderFragment<BankAccountRow> GetActionsTemplate()
    {
        return acc => __builder =>
        {
            <div class="d-flex gap-1">
                <GenericButtonComponent IconClass="bi bi-pencil"
                                       Variant="ButtonVariant.OutlineDarkBlue"
                                       Title="@L["Button.Edit"]"
                                       OnClick="@(() => HandleEdit(acc.Id))"
                                       CssClass="btn-square" />
                @if (!acc.IsPrimary)
                {
                    <GenericButtonComponent IconClass="bi bi-star"
                                           Variant="ButtonVariant.OutlineGray"
                                           Title="@L["Button.SetPrimary"]"
                                           OnClick="@(() => HandleSetPrimary(acc.Id))"
                                           CssClass="btn-square" />
                }
                <GenericButtonComponent IconClass="bi bi-trash"
                                       Variant="ButtonVariant.OutlineRed"
                                       Title="@L["Button.Delete"]"
                                       OnClick="@(() => HandleDelete(acc.Id))"
                                       CssClass="btn-square" />
            </div>
        };
    }

    protected override async Task OnParametersSetAsync()
    {
        var newId = EntityId ?? 0;
        if (newId > 0 && newId != _lastLoadedId)
            await LoadAsync(newId);
        else if (newId <= 0 && _lastLoadedId > 0)
            Clear();
    }

    public async Task LoadAsync(int entityId)
    {
        _lastLoadedId = entityId;
        accounts = EntityType switch
        {
            BankAccountEntityType.Customer =>
                (await CustomerBankAccountService.GetByCustomerIdAsync(entityId))
                    .Select(a => new BankAccountRow(a.Id, a.Bank?.BankName, a.BranchName, a.AccountNumber, a.AccountName, a.IsPrimary, null))
                    .ToList(),
            BankAccountEntityType.Supplier =>
                (await SupplierBankAccountService.GetBySupplierIdAsync(entityId))
                    .Select(a => new BankAccountRow(a.Id, a.Bank?.BankName, a.BranchName, a.AccountNumber, a.AccountName, a.IsPrimary, null))
                    .ToList(),
            BankAccountEntityType.Employee =>
                (await EmployeeBankAccountService.GetByEmployeeIdAsync(entityId))
                    .Select(a => new BankAccountRow(a.Id, a.Bank?.BankName, a.BranchName, a.AccountNumber, a.AccountName, a.IsPrimary, null))
                    .ToList(),
            BankAccountEntityType.Company =>
                (await CompanyBankAccountService.GetByCompanyIdAsync(entityId))
                    .Select(a => new BankAccountRow(a.Id, a.Bank?.BankName, a.BranchName, a.AccountNumber, a.AccountName, a.IsPrimary, a.Purpose))
                    .ToList(),
            _ => new()
        };
        StateHasChanged();
    }

    public void Clear()
    {
        _lastLoadedId = 0;
        accounts = new();
        StateHasChanged();
    }

    private void HandleAdd()
    {
        editingId = null;
        isModalVisible = true;
        StateHasChanged();
    }

    private void HandleEdit(int id)
    {
        editingId = id;
        isModalVisible = true;
        StateHasChanged();
    }

    private async Task HandleDelete(int id)
    {
        var result = EntityType switch
        {
            BankAccountEntityType.Customer => await CustomerBankAccountService.DeleteAsync(id),
            BankAccountEntityType.Supplier => await SupplierBankAccountService.DeleteAsync(id),
            BankAccountEntityType.Employee => await EmployeeBankAccountService.DeleteAsync(id),
            BankAccountEntityType.Company  => await CompanyBankAccountService.DeleteAsync(id),
            _ => ServiceResult.Failure("Unknown entity type")
        };

        if (result.IsSuccess)
        {
            accounts.RemoveAll(a => a.Id == id);
            await NotificationService.ShowSuccessAsync(L["Message.DeleteSuccess"].ToString());
            StateHasChanged();
        }
        else
        {
            await NotificationService.ShowErrorAsync(result.ErrorMessage ?? L["Message.DeleteFailed"].ToString());
        }
    }

    private async Task HandleSetPrimary(int id)
    {
        if (!EntityId.HasValue) return;
        var result = EntityType switch
        {
            BankAccountEntityType.Customer => await CustomerBankAccountService.SetPrimaryAsync(id, EntityId.Value),
            BankAccountEntityType.Supplier => await SupplierBankAccountService.SetPrimaryAsync(id, EntityId.Value),
            BankAccountEntityType.Employee => await EmployeeBankAccountService.SetPrimaryAsync(id, EntityId.Value),
            BankAccountEntityType.Company  => await CompanyBankAccountService.SetPrimaryAsync(id, EntityId.Value),
            _ => ServiceResult.Failure("Unknown entity type")
        };

        if (result.IsSuccess)
            await LoadAsync(EntityId.Value);
        else
            await NotificationService.ShowErrorAsync(result.ErrorMessage ?? L["Message.SaveFailed"].ToString());
    }

    private async Task HandleSaved()
    {
        isModalVisible = false;
        if (EntityId.HasValue)
            await LoadAsync(EntityId.Value);
    }
}
